6b9ab292fab06ecc22?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1451793601, "last_modified": 1776391123, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "oldcai", "last_touched": 1782823301, "title": "苹果电脑全线涨价，大家还会继续买吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1223840", "created": 1782784676, "deleted": 0, "content": "我有一台 2012 款 macbook pro ，现在还能跑。\r\n\r\n最近安装上 Claude Code ，勉强能跟上 AI 时代。\r\n\r\n不过，配置实在太老旧，brew 根本不敢更新。\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n打算换台笔记本，看中了 M5MAX + 2T + 128G ，\r\n\r\n没涨价前 4w 多，涨价后 5w 多，相差 6k 。\r\n\r\n感觉被劝退，待年底出 M6 ，再看看。\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n其实等 M6 ，是因为据说 macbook 要换模具，如果按照以前的逻辑，肯定买新不买旧。", "content_rendered": "<p>我有一台 2012 款 macbook pro ，现在还能跑。</p>\n<p>最近安装上 Claude Code ，勉强能跟上 AI 时代。</p>\n<p>不过，配置实在太老旧，brew 根本不敢更新。</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>打算换台笔记本，看中了 M5MAX + 2T + 128G ，</p>\n<p>没涨价前 4w 多，涨价后 5w 多，相差 6k 。</p>\n<p>感觉被劝退，待年底出 M6 ，再看看。</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>其实等 M6 ，是因为据说 macbook 要换模具，如果按照以前的逻辑，肯定买新不买旧。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1782784676, "replies": 110, "id": 1223840}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1768280127", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1768280127", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 23731, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3702, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 223061, "username": "377848", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/377848", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e617e52109162081597ac19f6165a055?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e617e52109162081597ac19f6165a055?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e617e52109162081597ac19f6165a055?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1490538352, "last_modified": 1753113897, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "wangfeng3769", "last_touched": 1782816539, "title": "广东农村堂弟不爱读书，中专/技校已经极限了，求建议：未来还有哪些相对靠谱的出路？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1223807", "created": 1782780792, "deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1782780962, "replies": 104, "id": 1223807}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 11163, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2375, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 115028, "username": "weberCd", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/weberCd", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7e72d865d48d685d8e1468d49e5a5223?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7e72d865d48d685d8e1468d49e5a5223?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7e72d865d48d685d8e1468d49e5a5223?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1430712890, "last_modified": 1782789707, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "karld", "last_touched": 1782824131, "title": "经济下行，我做了这些事情来节省开支，然后发现对生活品质几乎没有影响……欢迎补充", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1223876", "created": 1782789753, "deleted": 0, "content": "1.电信宽带降资费； 3 年合约期到了，我把电信宽带从 239/月降到了 109/月的低配套餐，无非就是带宽变小了，免费通话和赠送流量变少了，低配套餐实际使用下来，毫无体感上的区别；各地区政策可能不同，甚至携号转网换运营商可能省得更多。\r\n\r\n2.短途出行主要骑车或地铁，开车变少了。老油车了，油价高。久了习惯了，反而不想开车了，开支比公共交通更大，停车之类的也很麻烦。\r\n\r\n3.各类 App 的会员是越开越少了，而且是尽量和老婆共用 1 个会员。\r\n\r\n4.MacBook/iPhone 都主要考虑二手的了，特别是较老款的高配版，性价比很高；而且再次置换的时候，二手换二手，成本更低了。\r\n\r\n5.理发主要依靠快剪，12/次，不办卡，剪得快也节省时间，挺好。反而不想去普通理发店了。", "content_rendered": "<p>1.电信宽带降资费； 3 年合约期到了，我把电信宽带从 239/月降到了 109/月的低配套餐，无非就是带宽变小了，免费通话和赠送流量变少了，低配套餐实际使用下来，毫无体感上的区别；各地区政策可能不同，甚至携号转网换运营商可能省得更多。</p>\n<p>2.短途出行主要骑车或地铁，开车变少了。老油车了，油价高。久了习惯了，反而不想开车了，开支比公共交通更大，停车之类的也很麻烦。</p>\n<p>3.各类 App 的会员是越开越少了，而且是尽量和老婆共用 1 个会员。</p>\n<p>4.MacBook/iPhone 都主要考虑二手的了，特别是较老款的高配版，性价比很高；而且再次置换的时候，二手换二手，成本更低了。</p>\n<p>5.理发主要依靠快剪，12/次，不办卡，剪得快也节省时间，挺好。反而不想去普通理发店了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1782789753, "replies": 103, "id": 1223876}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1777132346", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1777132346", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 239561, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1777132346", "stars": 4497, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 479417, "username": "yuwancumian27149", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/yuwancumian27149", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/067a/7c6b/479417_mini.png?m=1732265906", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/067a/7c6b/479417_normal.png?m=1732265906", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/067a/7c6b/479417_large.png?m=1732265906", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/067a/7c6b/479417_xlarge.png?m=1732265906", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/067a/7c6b/479417_xxlarge.png?m=1732265906", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/067a/7c6b/479417_xxxlarge.png?m=1732265906", "created": 1585303453, "last_modified": 1732265906, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "NewMoorj", "last_touched": 1782823037, "title": "今年这是怎么了，各家✈️为啥都一直在抽风", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1223810", "created": 1782781717, "deleted": 0, "content": "想问下了解情况的，为啥今年开始，怎么大部分机场都时好时坏，比如我自己，用的是花云，一个月 60 块也不便宜了，为啥这么久了，还是处理不好呢，其他家的好像也大都如此，今年开始陆陆续续都不行了", "content_rendered": "想问下了解情况的，为啥今年开始，怎么大部分机场都时好时坏，比如我自己，用的是花云，一个月 60 块也不便宜了，为啥这么久了，还是处理不好呢，其他家的好像也大都如此，今年开始陆陆续续都不行了", "last_modified": 1782781717, "replies": 77, "id": 1223810}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 71807, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9721, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 599108, "username": "morota", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/morota", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/79f4/a825/599108_mini.png?m=1712121642", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/79f4/a825/599108_normal.png?m=1712121642", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/79f4/a825/599108_large.png?m=1712121642", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/79f4/a825/599108_xlarge.png?m=1712121642", "created": 1666777043, "last_modified": 1712121642, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "OvO88", "last_touched": 1782818700, "title": "兄弟们， deepseek 配合哪个编程工具最好用，有亲身体验的来说说", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1223806", "created": 1782780330, "deleted": 0, "content": "DeepSeek-TUI ，Reasonix ，Codex ，ClaudeCode ，OpenCode, PI\r\n用来编程，哪个更省钱，缓存命中更好，完成工作不差的。\r\n或者上面没列出来的也行。", "content_rendered": "<p>DeepSeek-TUI ，Reasonix ，Codex ，ClaudeCode ，OpenCode, PI\n用来编程，哪个更省钱，缓存命中更好，完成工作不差的。\n或者上面没列出来的也行。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1782780330, "replies": 73, "id": 1223806}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/df0a/ab05/1148_l